data.description: Beautiful private home on Tracyton Blvd sits on 1.04 acres with peekaboo water views. Check out this 1,562 sq ft, 3 bed/1 bath rambler with all the updates you would ever want. Updated kitchen, mud room, and laundry room. New doors, paint inside and out with updates to the bathroom. 11x13 storage shed with electricity. 2 car detached garage with RV parking. Enjoy the open and private patio off the dining room. Mature landscaping throughout the property to include fruit trees. Excellent location close to Silverdale, hospital, shopping, and the coveted Central Kitsap School District. Welcome Home!
